<b>Alma:</b> "What was he like?"
<b>Jonah:</b> "Simon was... <b>brave</b>. The bravest man I may ever know."
<b>Jonah:</b> "A hard nut to crack, too. Quiet. Brooding. A real to himself type, you know?"
<b>Alma:</b> (I can imagine.)
<b>Jonah:</b> "But when you got to know him, he was rather kind. Could be <b>sweet</b>, even. Patient with kids, chivalrous... I'm not sure what else to say."

